divs: Sighting DetailsLast night on the sky above Sabac - Serbia,my friend and some other people have seen about 50 UFO in small formations.We are still scared. I have 33 photos all some kind of dots and lines,only on one that I have from my cellphone is strange circle. This is not joke, I am serious 49 years old man.I have never experienced something like this in my life.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Šabac
